OL,3,CPost Office chairman steps down amid
OL,4,CHorizon scandal fallout
OL,6,FThe chairman of the Post Office has
OL,7,Fstepped down amid ongoing tensions in
OL,8,Fthe wake of the Horizon IT scandal.
OL,10,FHenry Staunton will depart from the
OL,11,Frole following a phone call with
OL,12,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch on
OL,13,FSaturday.
OL,15,FMs Badenoch said she "felt there was a
OL,16,Fneed for new leadership" as the
OL,17,Fcompany remains under heightened
OL,18,Fscrutiny over the wrongful prosecution
OL,19,Fof hundreds of subpostmasters.
