OL,3,CPost Office chairman steps down amid
OL,4,CHorizon scandal fallout
OL,6,FAn interim will be appointed
OL,7,F"shortly", the Department for Business
OL,8,Fand Trade said.
OL,10,FMr Staunton only took up the post at
OL,11,Fthe state-owned business in December
OL,12,F2022, following nine years as chairman
OL,13,Fof WH Smith.
OL,15,FHe had been tasked with leading the
OL,16,Fboard of directors as the business
OL,17,Freels from the fallout of what has
OL,18,Fbeen described as the UK's biggest
OL,19,Fmiscarriage of justice.
